{"tid":2185733,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是靚晚 甜記餃子","createTime":"2020-09-02T12:45:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-05T03:43:20.000Z","uid":310853,"like":22,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f9b71635813f8145e94b861d6fb91ea0f3bf54b0","tid":2185733,"uid":310853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T12:45:25.000Z","msg":"話說原本今日想食嗰間串燒行到過去未開<br />\n之後諗住轉元州牛肉麵或者甜記餃子<br />\n最後都幾耐冇食過餃子 就揀咗甜記餃子<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cJqQhuW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcJqQhuW.png&h=7e751607&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hh7jaQr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhh7jaQr.png&h=a4e4994b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雙拼煎餃 - $46/10隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pgsCGXm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpgsCGXm.png&h=53b0b5b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香芹芫荽豬肉餃<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n作為芫荽愛好者嘅我 依個係首選<br />\n咬落係夠芫荽 仲好重芫荽味添<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/277jaRF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F277jaRF.png&h=47280b4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n粟米芝士雞肉餃<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗住揀個特別少少 食落去都一樣足料 <br />\n之前未食過粟米餃 咬落去個口感好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X2yZaTt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX2yZaTt.png&h=4127ef92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iiq8OFt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fiiq8OFt.png&h=44abc211&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後仲有嗌咗個牛展麵 雞湯底 - $40<br />\n<br />\n依個價錢都相當優惠 d料都足 冇偷雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n牛展厚實 雖然唔算相當淋身<br />\n但絕對係輕鬆咬得開<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一開始諗 牛展 + 雞湯底 會唔會怪 但食落去係ok的<br />\n麵底我唔知佢用咩麵底 但幾啱我食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pw1gc9T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpw1gc9T.jpg&h=e71bb057&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n啱先冇影到餐牌 上網偷咗落嚟比大家睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ffa62d8dc648a23c694ace85f1df047063283a8","tid":2185733,"uid":260581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T12:49:44.000Z","msg":"你拎到返屋企 <br />\n出曬倒汗水 望落焗淋左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74dfb338b3d91aec3a2749bf51212186a9928ba8","tid":2185733,"uid":310853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ffa62d8dc648a23c694ace85f1df047063283a8","tid":2185733,"uid":260581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T12:49:44.000Z","msg":"你拎到返屋企 <br />\n出曬倒汗水 望落焗淋左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T12:51:01.000Z","msg":"十五分鐘左右路程 未淋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"679b4d456557ab9bba347dfa8ee56545834f7160","tid":2185733,"uid":263223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T12:54:02.000Z","msg":"之前食過佢嘅醉雞幾好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b84162146643a7d2dc1d4dea30b034a9bdb876b5","tid":2185733,"uid":299794,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T12:59:52.000Z","msg":"佢啲菜脯好好食！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b4a4c2784fe9e16a399c3ff746bcafc2bf71676","tid":2185733,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T13:13:27.000Z","msg":"菜脯好似幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe8fdb3de04e68174dc826fb7f4dbdaee30d41c9","tid":2185733,"uid":86119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T13:14:18.000Z","msg":"識食 上次吉寸今次甜記<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過甜記得湯餃好食煎就麻撚麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每次都叫蕃茄薯仔湯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好好飲"},{"pid":"600bb1e2a9526658833e425fb088735b8863ea07","tid":2185733,"uid":310853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe8fdb3de04e68174dc826fb7f4dbdaee30d41c9","tid":2185733,"uid":86119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T13:14:18.000Z","msg":"識食 上次吉寸今次甜記<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過甜記得湯餃好食煎就麻撚麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每次都叫蕃茄薯仔湯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好好飲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T13:23:11.000Z","msg":"見d人講完我就去試下咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c100928a261bbf29b804a36b7986d5caff302b4","tid":2185733,"uid":310853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b4a4c2784fe9e16a399c3ff746bcafc2bf71676","tid":2185733,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T13:13:27.000Z","msg":"菜脯好似幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T13:23:22.000Z","msg":"唔差"},{"pid":"e3948dfaea55a3d95b0de267a4a86d1c5dba9663","tid":2185733,"uid":272819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T13:29:14.000Z","msg":"正"},{"pid":"9022e1b929f8d3e70197d889af7f34a555783d54","tid":2185733,"uid":102997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T14:12:17.000Z","msg":"芫茜10隻蕃茄魚湯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14129f32f94df97ac26fc92fc49b300ef944aef3","tid":2185733,"uid":58623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T14:12:22.000Z","msg":"啲鴨舌好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c34013a1f5530c58b94283c62f2c25e31ef3915","tid":2185733,"uid":51583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T14:13:26.000Z","msg":"每星期都食"},{"pid":"60d5e2d33c5ce55ddfe9f38ed72a65c47eabedc6","tid":2185733,"uid":260581,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T14:20:48.000Z","msg":"Sorry 借個位<br />\n有冇人幫我推一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n越煮越好條友 越黎越痴線<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2173277\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2173277</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"61dbb2076503b01097a9ee7774764878ebc81bb8","tid":2185733,"uid":288764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T14:20:53.000Z","msg":"煎洋蔥牛肉餃好好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33689676c805df38288283e46758f6ae32a1c7ba","tid":2185733,"uid":8435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T15:36:53.000Z","msg":"以前放lunch要行15分鐘都要過去食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"925877d4ba108b183c9bb23da20b0b835142a98c","tid":2185733,"uid":191812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T03:29:55.000Z","msg":"羊肉餃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6e4bf09679e9d9dafb9a411039ea7ef0fe6892a","tid":2185733,"uid":349052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T03:43:20.000Z","msg":"芝士雞肉餃好出色"}]}